readme:
# Trainz Game Script language support in Atom
[![macOS Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/jenolan/atom-language-trainz-script.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/jenolan/atom-language-trainz-script)
[![Windows Build Status](https://ci.appveyor.com/api/projects/status/fietyme7mt9m5r0s?svg=true)](https://ci.appveyor.com/project/jenolan/atom-language-trainz-script/branch/master)
[![Dependency Status](https://david-dm.org/jenolan/atom-language-trainz-script.svg)](https://david-dm.org/jenolan/atom-language-trainz-script)

Adds syntax highlighting and snippets to Trainz Game Script files in Atom.

Contributions are greatly appreciated. Please fork this repository and open a
pull request to add snippets, make grammar tweaks, etc.
